# UI Design System

Inspired by GitHub, Linear, Stripe, Vercel, Notion — professional SaaS only.

## Banned Patterns

- No AI gradients, neon colors, or purple AI aesthetics
- No glassmorphism, glowing cards, floating blobs
- No animated backgrounds or decorative-only motion

## Required

- shadcn/ui + Tailwind + Radix + Lucide
- 8px spacing system, rounded-xl, clean borders, subtle shadows
- Single accent color: blue only
- Dark theme: #09090B background, #18181B cards, #27272A borders
- CRM/dashboard feel: Linear × Notion × GitHub Projects
- WCAG-compliant contrast, focus states, keyboard navigation
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`
